reviewText: This documentary was a good overview covering the career of Amy Winehouse through the Back in Black release.  Not as satisfying as the in-depth profile presented in the recent theatrical release of 'Amy', but still quite good.
A&E Biography always does quality work. Amy was a superb artist, I really wish she would have survived. Also check out "The Day She Came To Dingle"....
